Name: Dizzy Two
About the game: This is a legendary quest from the 80s, invented by the Oliver Twins, about a yolkfolk living in trees. The main character, Dizzy, constantly rescues relatives who get into trouble. And now he found himself on a strange island after his family was kidnapped by the Hunter. To save the Dizzy family, you need to communicate with the characters, as well as collect and use various items.
